The foyer opens to the formal dining room and large family room with fireplace which leads you to the beautiful kitchen and breakfast nook. The fifth bedroom and full bath completes the first floor. The second floor features 4 Bedrooms, including a King-sized Master suite with sitting area, large walk in closet, dual vanities, garden tub, separate shower and more!!
